---
---

<section class="bg-surface-low py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-3xl text-white mb-3">Unmatched Lean Performance</h2>
      <p class="font-label text-muted uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Runtime footprint comparison (KB)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-end max-w-3xl mx-auto h-[300px]">
      <!-- Prisma -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 h-full justify-end group">
        <div class="w-full bg-surface-mid h-[85%] rounded-t-lg relative transition-all group-hover:bg-surface-high">
          <span class="absolute -top-7 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 font-label text-xs text-muted">~1.6 MB</span>
        </div>
        <span class="font-label text-xs text-muted">Prisma</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Drizzle -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 h-full justify-end group">
        <div class="w-full bg-surface-mid h-[22%] rounded-t-lg relative transition-all group-hover:bg-surface-high">
          <span class="absolute -top-7 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 font-label text-xs text-muted">~7.4 KB</span>
        </div>
        <span class="font-label text-xs text-muted">Drizzle</span>
      </div>

      <!-- sqlcx -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 h-full justify-end group">
        <div class="w-full primary-gradient h-[2%] rounded-t-lg relative shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(213,251,42,0.4)]">
          <span class="absolute -top-7 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 font-headline font-bold text-xs text-lime">0 KB</span>
        </div>
        <span class="font-label text-xs text-white font-bold">sqlcx</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center max-w-xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-muted text-sm italic">"By moving all logic to the build step, sqlcx eliminates the middleman. Your production binary only contains your SQL and the driver connection."</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
